ep 04:10 (verificar uso cpu linux)\n\n\n$ DISPLAY=192.168.1.128:0.0; export DISPLAY\n\n*Yum comandos\n yum list installed | grep wget (listar paquetes instalados)\n \n\nproxy red hat sin user ni pass \n\nexport http_proxy=\"http://username:p@s#w:E@server:port/\"\nwget example.com\n        --2011-03-15 03:30:51--  http://example.com/\n        Resolving s... failed: Name or service not known.\n        wget: unable to resolve host address âsâ\nexport http_proxy=\"10.10.10.16:8080\"\n\n\nBACKUPS (elimina backup generados por oracle)\n\n<br>find /data03/backups/amlprod/bkp/ -mindepth 1 -mtime +1 -exec rm -fr {} \\;\n<br>find /data03/backups/autoconsulta/db/ -mindepth 1 -mtime +1 -exec rm -fr {} \\;\n<br>find /data03/backups/autoconsulta/arch/ -mindepth 1 -mtime +1 -exec rm -fr {} \\;\n<br>find /data03/backups/sunprod/backup_prod/ -mindepth 1 -mtime +7 -exec rm -fr {} \\;\n<br>find /data03/backups/cyprusdb/db/ -mindepth 1 -mtime +2 -exec rm -fr {} \\;\n<br>find /data03/backups/cyprusdbdes/db/ -mindepth 1 -mtime +2 -exec rm -fr {} \\;\n<br>find /data03/backups/sundestest/CEDE12/ -mindepth 1 -mtime +1 -exec rm -fr {} \\;\n<br>find /data03/backups/sundestest/CENT12/ -mindepth 1 -mtime +1 -exec rm -fr {} \\;\n<br>find /data03/backups/cyprus/test/ -mindepth 1 -mtime +1 -exec rm -fr {} \\;\n<br>find /data03/backups/autoconsulta/ -mindepth 1 -mtime +1 -exec rm -fr {} \\; \n\nreiniciar cron solaris 10\nsvcadm restart cron\n\n<br>Cambio de hora linux debian\nsudo dpkg-reconfigure tzdata o tzselect\n\n\n<br>Current default time zone: \'America/Argentina/Buenos_\nAires\'\n<br>Local time is now:      Sat Nov 21 10:52:15 -03 2020.\n<br>Universal Time is now:  Sat Nov 21 13:52:15 UTC 2020.\n\n\n[[:Media:Aplicando-al-LPIC1_Examen101.pdf]]','utf-8'),(237,'\n[[File:linux.jpeg|frame|500px]]\n\n[[File:permisoslinux.jpeg|right|300px|caption]]\n\nBACKUPS:\n\n* Realizar backup con tar.gz\ntar czf backup-$(date +\'%F\').tar.gz /home/* \n*Backup + excluir extensiones\ntar -czvf mibackup.tar.